From: Martin Schiller <ms@dev.tdt.de>
Date: Tue, 2 Dec 2025 09:48:07 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] clk: mxl: Fix CGU_GATE3 value

Set the correct address for CGU_GATE3. This fixes a copy&paste issue.

Fixes: d058fd9e8984 ("clk: intel: Add CGU clock driver for a new SoC")
Signed-off-by: Martin Schiller <ms@dev.tdt.de>
---
 drivers/clk/x86/clk-lgm.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/clk/x86/clk-lgm.c b/drivers/clk/x86/clk-lgm.c
index f69455dd1c98..e1a4fcfda8f4 100644
--- a/drivers/clk/x86/clk-lgm.c
+++ b/drivers/clk/x86/clk-lgm.c
@@ -109,7 +109,7 @@
 #define CGU_GATE0		0x300
 #define CGU_GATE1		0x310
 #define CGU_GATE2		0x320
-#define CGU_GATE3		0x310
+#define CGU_GATE3		0x330
 
 #define PLL_DIV(x)		((x) + 0x04)
 #define PLL_SSC(x)		((x) + 0x10)
